M +1 345 324 0887




Brendan Barry has served as Chief Underwriting Officer since August 2011. Prior to that, Brendan was Senior Vice President since September 2006 when he joined Greenlight Re. Brendan has over 20 years experience in the property and casualty insurance and reinsurance industry. He has previously served as Vice President of Platinum Underwriters (Bermuda) Ltd. and Senior Underwriter for Hannover Reinsurance (Ireland) Ltd. where he managed a diversified portfolio of reinsurance transactions. Brendan holds a Bachelor of Arts from the National College of Ireland, a post graduate diploma in statistics from Dublin University (Trinity College) and an MBA from Smurfit School of Business (University College Dublin).







