								ASSET MANAGEMENT STRATEGY
								




Our investment portfolio is managed by DME Advisors,LP("DAE") a value-oriented investment advisor that analyzes companies’ available financial data in an effort to identify undervalued and overvalued securities. DME aims to protect capital while finding investment opportunities that generate positive returns. We provide our historical investment returns on our website, (www.greenlightre.com) where we also post our monthly investment returns, our largest disclosed long positions and our long short exposures as of the end of each month.

 



