								Greenlight Re Adds Claims Management Expertise
								




									16 Jan 2016
									
									Greenlight Re has strengthened its Grand Cayman team with the hiring of Troy Galley as the head of claims.  Mr. Galley is a veteran in the insurance industry with over 25 years of experience in multiple lines of business.  Mr. Galley joins Greenlight Re from Great American Insurance Group where he worked for the past 28 years in various roles, including most recently as the Divisional Vice President of Great American’s Claim Resolution Services.
									



